                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="en">Fair value according to §194 BauGB (in thousands of euros).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="fr">Juste valeur selon §194 BauGB (dans thousands de euros).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="nl">Reële waarde volgens §194 BauGB (in thousands van euros).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="es">Valor razonable según §194 BauGB (en miles de euros).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="it">Valore equo secondo §194 BauGB (in migliaia di euro).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="cs">Reálná hodnota podle §194 BauGB (v tisících eur).</xs:documentation>
                                          <xs:documentation xml:lang="hu">Valós érték a §194 BauGB szerint (ezer euróban).</xs:documentation>
